data.description: FOR COMP PURPOSES ONLY: This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is set on nearly 1/4 acre in the desirable Hanson area of 29 Palms! Pleasant landscaping and a welcoming facade greet you as you approach from the paved drive. Upon entering, you'll find yourself in a spacious open concept living area with inviting fireplace, vaulted ceilings, tile floors and plenty of natural light. The kitchen has been finely appointed with gorgeous countertops and cabinetry, full tile backsplash, an island with bar seating and a gas stove for the serious chef! Moving on to the bedrooms, you'll find both of the guest bedrooms to be generously sized, while the guest bath has everything you need with its shower/tub combo. The large master bedroom enjoys its own mini-split for zoned heating and cooling, while the master bath features dual sinks and a shower/tub combo. An attached 2 car garage and energy efficient mini-splits for climate control throughout the home round out practical matters. Not to leave out the outdoor living space, the huge backyard is fully fenced and has a nice concrete patio with shade ramada - perfect for taking in the nearby views of the mountains of Joshua Tree National Park. Last but not least, you'll love knowing this special find is only 5 minutes from both the amenities of town and the gates of the national park - WOW!
